content: Wanted to welcome all CG Connectathon participants. Looking forward to a great couple of days.
For anyone who hasn't reviewed it in a while, here is our track: http://wiki.hl7.org/index.php?title=201809_Clinical_Genomics

Hi all CG attendees - I have updated the Agenda with the ballot comments we will be discussing in various quarters. I am not sure they will all get done, but everyone we get through (discuss, determine a resolution, and vote) is great!
https://confluence.hl7.org/display/CGW/2018-09+CG+WGM+Minutes
